@glenn-jocher Great job!!! It work!
I still have a question about accuracy. I am testing for counting the number of identical objects in a photo. When testing on pure darknet on a test image, I get 73 objects with img-size 32 * 32 = 1024px. On your version with the same settings, the result is 27 objects, but it works several times faster. 
May be you have any thought why such a difference in accuracy?
